<i>they begin construction</i>
<i>on a fort made of pillows.</i>

71
00:03:09,188 --> 00:03:11,817
<i>Its name: New Fluffytown.</i>

72
00:03:11,817 --> 00:03:15,112
<i>Its goal: to be a newer,</i>
<i>fluffier town than Fluffytown,</i>

73
00:03:15,112 --> 00:03:17,656
