<i>from the previous year.</i>

74
00:03:17,656 --> 00:03:20,659
HARRY:
<i>New Fluffytown</i>
<i>didn't care who you were.</i>

75
00:03:20,659 --> 00:03:24,538
<i>You were surrounded by</i>
<i>softness.</i>

76
00:03:24,538 --> 00:03:27,415
<i>It's just like</i>
<i>crawling through a hug.</i>

77
00:03:27,415 --> 00:03:33,463
Well, I guess all hugs
have to come to an end.

78
00:03:33,463 --> 00:03:36,341
<i>When an opportunity arises</i>
<i>for a world record,</i>

79
00:03:36,341 --> 00:03:38,259
<i>it creates a rift.</i>

80
00:03:38,259 --> 00:03:40,179
<i>Troy wants to</i>
<i>go for the record,</i>

81
00:03:40,179 --> 00:03:42,890
<i>using blankets</i>
<i>for rapid expansion.</i>

82
00:03:42,890 --> 00:03:44,850
<i>Abed insists on pillows,</i>

83
00:03:44,850 --> 00:03:47,227
<i>declaring world records</i>
<i>to be dumb.</i>

84
00:03:47,227 --> 00:03:49,354
<i>Troy declares</i>
<i>the declaration lame,</i>

85
00:03:49,354 --> 00:03:52,649
<i>stating that thinking records</i>
<i>are dumb is stupid.</i>

86
00:03:52,649 --> 00:03:54,902
<i>He secedes from New Fluffytown</i>

87
00:03:54,902 --> 00:03:57,029
<i>and begins constructing</i>
<i>Blanketsburg</i>

88
00:03:57,029 --> 00:03:58,321
<i>on the other side of campus.</i>

89
00:03:58,321 --> 00:04:00,574
<i>Abed renames his fort</i>
<i>Pillowtown</i>

90
00:04:00,574 --> 00:04:02,450
<i>for the sake of</i>
<i>conceptual symmetry.</i>

91
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:06,997
<i>Both forts expand until both</i>
<i>are in each other's way.</i>

92
00:04:06,997 --> 00:04:09,083
<i>Study Room F, 3 p.m.,</i>

