<i>things reach</i>
<i>their boiling point.</i>

94
00:04:11,043 --> 00:04:12,669
STAR-BURNS:
You stand back.

95
00:04:12,669 --> 00:04:14,963
PELTON: Watch it, Star-Burns.
My name is Alex!

96
00:04:14,963 --> 00:04:16,339
[WOMAN SCREAMS]

97
00:04:16,339 --> 00:04:18,008
<i>A softly lobbed,</i>

98
