103
00:04:31,230 --> 00:04:34,108
Star-Burns, go.
STAR-BURNS: Excuse me, please.

104
00:04:34,108 --> 00:04:37,360
Hold. Hold.
Jeffrey. Jeffrey, find me.

105
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,612
TROY: Get back.
PELTON: Jeffrey!

106
00:04:38,612 --> 00:04:40,030
