108
00:04:42,116 --> 00:04:43,491
ABED:
<i>Protect Pillowtown.</i>

109
00:04:43,491 --> 00:04:45,160
Jeffrey. You're not mediating.

110
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:47,079
Dean, what do you want me
to say, huh?

111
00:04:47,079 --> 00:04:48,789
Some conflicts
are so pointless,

