137
00:06:01,528 --> 00:06:02,946
That's right, Jackson.

138
00:06:03,822 --> 00:06:05,073
<i>Silence.</i>

139
00:06:05,073 --> 00:06:06,491
NARRATOR:
<i>Midnight comes,</i>

140
00:06:06,491 --> 00:06:08,535
<i>and a campus holds its breath.</i>

141
00:06:08,535 --> 00:06:10,662
MAN [ON RADIO]:
<i>There's a lot of blanket</i>
<i>stackers</i>

142
00:06:10,662 --> 00:06:13,540
<i>and pillow packers</i>
<i>thinking it's gonna go down.</i>

143
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:14,833
<i>But there's a lot of us folks</i>

144
00:06:14,833 --> 00:06:16,960
<i>from the scene</i>
