156
00:06:43,402 --> 00:06:45,697
NARRATOR:
<i>12:07 a.m.,</i>

157
00:06:45,697 --> 00:06:48,407
<i>Blanketsburg soldiers charge a</i>
<i>pillow fort in the library.</i>

158
00:06:48,407 --> 00:06:51,036
<i>The Pillowtonians move quickly</i>
<i>to defend.</i>

159
00:06:51,036 --> 00:06:53,496
SHIRLEY:
<i>There were no rules in that</i>
<i>first battle.</i>

160
00:06:53,496 --> 00:06:55,414
<i>You hit someone,</i>
<i>and if they went down,</i>

161
00:06:55,414 --> 00:06:57,376
