169
00:07:18,646 --> 00:07:22,525
TROY [OVER PA]:
<i>Citizens of Blanketsburg,</i>

170
00:07:22,525 --> 00:07:26,529
<i>I ask you now</i>
<i>to prepare for war.</i>

171
00:07:26,529 --> 00:07:30,909
<i>And I ask Garrett to please fix</i>
<i>the microphone on my laptop.</i>

172
00:07:30,909 --> 00:07:32,911
<i>It's doing that thing again.</i>

173
00:07:35,956 --> 00:07:37,791
NARRATOR:
<i>The United Forts of Pillowtown</i>

