<i>of Blanketsburg are at war.</i>

175
00:07:40,710 --> 00:07:45,173
<i>Each side attempting to kick</i>
<i>down and replace the other.</i>

176
00:07:45,173 --> 00:07:46,925
<i>The unmoving line</i>
<i>between them</i>

177
00:07:46,925 --> 00:07:49,594
<i>is a campus-wide,</i>
<i>fleece-laden strip</i>

178
00:07:49,594 --> 00:07:52,806
<i>of pillow-to-pillow combat.</i>

179
00:07:52,806 --> 00:07:54,433
<i>Britta Perry attempts</i>
<i>to capture</i>

180
00:07:54,433 --> 00:07:58,019
<i>the war's sublime indignities</i>
<i>on film.</i>

181
00:07:58,019 --> 00:08:01,564
<i>Unfortunately for Britta</i>
<i>and photographers like her,</i>

182
00:08:01,564 --> 00:08:03,691
