186
00:08:11,325 --> 00:08:12,659
<i>Outside the science lab,</i>

187
00:08:12,659 --> 00:08:14,619
<i>at the Battle</i>
<i>of Big Bulletin Board,</i>

188
00:08:14,619 --> 00:08:17,956
<i>Pierce Hawthorne suffers</i>
<i>broken glasses, a hurt finger</i>

189
00:08:17,956 --> 00:08:19,540
<i>and erectile dysfunction.</i>

190
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:21,084
